column5: Since the June opener , I,ve caught a few muskies,was also in boat for a couple of tanks caught by friends,caught tons of smallies,and even a few accidents....hope you enjoy.
Very nice work so far, Larry....keep it up!
Those are some monster smallies ! Good going!
Those muskies are fatter than the carp!  Great trophy fish!
Wow Nice surprise !!! was it your target to catch that Sturgeon....Great photos Larry
Spectacular fish and photos, Larry. You seem to have every available species dialed in. Congrats on another epic month!
Great June Larry !!! Thanks for makeing me drool
What's going on with the mouth of the sturgeon?  The mouth area looks like, not a mouth at all.  Wow, just realized those creatures of very different yaps, never saw that before.
Nice smallies Larry....  They're so fat...lol
Dam!  Thats a great June Larry!!!!  Looks like a season for me minus the sturgon
